rows.label: qst202507_msg0001
rows.name:
You're amazing, KOS-MOS Re:! Hey,
where does all that power come from?

rows.label: qst202507_msg0002
rows.name:
What's your power source? How
do you replenish your energy?

rows.label: qst202507_msg0003
rows.name:
Can you control the output?
Is there any strain on
your biological parts?

rows.label: qst202507_msg0004
rows.name: My apologies, Astelle.

rows.label: qst202507_msg0005
rows.name: I am unable to answer those questions.

rows.label: qst202507_msg0006
rows.name: Eh? Why?

rows.label: qst202507_msg0007
rows.name:
I judge that there is no need to
answer anyone other than my Driver.

rows.label: qst202507_msg0008
rows.name:
Aww, you could tell me a
little, couldn't you?

rows.label: qst202507_msg0009
rows.name: My apologies.

rows.label: qst202507_msg0010
rows.name: You really can't?

rows.label: qst202507_msg0011
rows.name: I cannot.

rows.label: qst202507_msg0012
rows.name: Hmph.

rows.label: qst202507_msg0013
rows.name:
Hehe, you really are
an interesting one.

rows.label: qst202507_msg0014
rows.name:
Hey, would you mind if I
touched your clothes and such?

rows.label: qst202507_msg0015
rows.name: Yes, that would be acceptable.

rows.label: qst202507_msg0016
rows.name: Really!

rows.label: qst202507_msg0017
rows.name: Hmm, so this is how it's made.

rows.label: qst202507_msg0018
rows.name: Hey, can I take this off?

rows.label: qst202507_msg0019
rows.name: I have no objection, but...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202507_msg0020
rows.name:
it would expose my internal
frame, which may violate
public standards of decency.

rows.label: qst202507_msg0021
rows.name:
Hmph, is that so? Well,
it should be fine.

rows.label: qst202507_msg0022
rows.name:
W-Wait a minute, you
can't, Astelle-san!

rows.label: qst202507_msg0023
rows.name:
You can't just strip
her clothes off here!

rows.label: qst202507_msg0024
rows.name:
Eh? But KOS-MOS Re: said
she didn't mind...[ML:Dash ]

rows.label: qst202507_msg0025
rows.name: It's not okay!

rows.label: qst202507_msg0026
rows.name:
Stop playing around and
let's go see Emperor Nefer!

rows.label: qst202507_msg0027
rows.name: Aww, no fun.
